<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Nissan Saudi Arabia × Infobip | Case Study</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="../assets/infobip-logo.png" />

<style>
:root{
  --blue:#1a56ff;
  --blue-light:#4b7fff;
  --blue-dim:rgba(26,86,255,0.12);
  --gold:#e8b86d;
  --dark:#0f1e38;
  --dark2:#162240;
  --dark3:#1c2e50;
  --surface:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  --surface2:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  --border2:rgba(26,86,255,0.25);
  --text:#f0f4ff;
  --text-dim:#8898bb;
  --text-dimmer:#4d5e80;
  --radius:18px;
  --radius-sm:10px;
}

*{ box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }

html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }

body{
  font-family:'Syne','Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;
  background:var(--dark);
  color:var(--text);
  overflow-x:hidden;
  line-height:1.6;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   GLOBAL BG MESH
══════════════════════════════ */
body::before{
  content:'';
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 10% 0%, rgba(26,86,255,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 90% 100%, rgba(26,86,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 50% 50%, rgba(26,86,255,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events:none;
  z-index:0;
}

/* grid overlay */
body::after{
  content:'';
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size:72px 72px;
  pointer-events:none;
  z-index:0;
}

.page-wrapper{
  position:relative;
  z-index:1;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   LAYOUT
══════════════════════════════ */
.container{
  max-width:1180px;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:0 40px;
}

section{ padding:90px 40px; max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   HERO
══════════════════════════════ */
.hero{
  position:relative;
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  overflow:hidden;
  padding:0;
}

/* Hero dramatic background */
.hero-bg{
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 80% at 60% 50%, rgba(26,86,255,0.22) 0%, transparent 65%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 80% at 0% 100%, rgba(26,86,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
    linear-gradient(160deg, #050a18 0%, #070e22 40%, #0c1a3f 100%);
  z-index:0;
}

/* animated diagonal lines */
.hero-lines{
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  overflow:hidden;
  z-index:0;
  pointer-events:none;
}
.hero-lines::before,
.hero-lines::after{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  width:1px;
  height:200%;
  top:-50%;
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(26,86,255,0.25), rgba(26,86,255,0.4), rgba(26,86,255,0.1), transparent);
  animation:scanline 8s linear infinite;
}
.hero-lines::before{ left:30%; animation-delay:-3s; opacity:.5; }
.hero-lines::after{ right:22%; width:2px; animation-delay:-1s; opacity:.3; }

@keyframes scanline{
  0%{ transform:rotate(15deg) translateX(-200px); }
  100%{ transform:rotate(15deg) translateX(200px); }
}

/* Large blurred circle */
.hero-orb{
  position:absolute;
  width:700px; height:700px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,86,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
  right:-180px; top:-120px;
  filter:blur(40px);
  animation:breathe 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  pointer-events:none;
}
.hero-orb2{
  position:absolute;
  width:400px; height:400px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(75,127,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  left:10%; bottom:0;
  filter:blur(60px);
  animation:breathe 9s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  pointer-events:none;
}
@keyframes breathe{
  0%,100%{ transform:scale(1); opacity:1; }
  50%{ transform:scale(1.15); opacity:.7; }
}

.hero-content{
  position:relative;
  z-index:2;
  padding:140px 0 100px;
  width:100%;
}

.hero-inner{
  max-width:1180px;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:0 40px;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:60px;
  align-items:center;
}

.hero-logos{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:16px;
  margin-bottom:32px;
}
.logo-badge{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:10px;
  backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
}
.logo-badge img{
  height:52px;
  object-fit:contain;
  filter:none;
  opacity:1;
}
.logo-badge .logo-nissan{
  height:70px;
}

.hero-tag{
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
  padding:7px 18px;
  background:var(--blue-dim);
  border:1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius:50px;
  font-size:12px;
  font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:1px;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--blue-light);
  margin-bottom:24px;
}
.hero-tag::before{
  content:'';
  width:6px;height:6px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--blue-light);
  animation:pulse 2s infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse{
  0%,100%{ opacity:1; box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(75,127,255,0.6); }
  50%{ opacity:.7; box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(75,127,255,0); }
}

h1{
  font-size:clamp(36px,4.5vw,62px);
  font-weight:800;
  line-height:1.08;
  letter-spacing:-1.5px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
  color:#fff;
}
h1 .accent{ color:var(--blue-light); }
h1 .line2{ display:block; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-weight:600; }

.hero-sub{
  font-size:16px;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  line-height:1.7;
  max-width:480px;
  margin-bottom:36px;
}

.hero-cta-row{
  display:flex;
  gap:14px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.btn-primary{
  padding:14px 32px;
  background:var(--blue);
  color:#fff;
  border:none;
  border-radius:50px;
  font-size:14px;
  font-weight:700;
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  letter-spacing:.3px;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:.2s;
  text-decoration:none;
  display:inline-block;
  box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(26,86,255,0.4);
}
.btn-primary:hover{ background:var(--blue-light); transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 14px 40px rgba(26,86,255,0.5); }

.btn-ghost{
  padding:14px 32px;
  background:transparent;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  border:1.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:50px;
  font-size:14px;
  font-weight:600;
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:.2s;
  text-decoration:none;
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
}
.btn-ghost:hover{ border-color:var(--blue-light); color:var(--blue-light); }

/* Hero right: stats cluster */
.hero-right{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:14px;
}

.hero-stat-cluster{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:14px;
}

.hero-kpi{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:22px 24px;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  transition:.25s;
}
.hero-kpi::before{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,86,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
  opacity:0;
  transition:.3s;
}
.hero-kpi:hover{ border-color:var(--border2); transform:translateY(-3px); }
.hero-kpi:hover::before{ opacity:1; }

.hero-kpi .kpi-val{
  font-size:40px;
  font-weight:800;
  color:#fff;
  line-height:1;
  letter-spacing:-1px;
  margin-bottom:4px;
}
.hero-kpi .kpi-val .unit{
  font-size:22px;
  color:var(--blue-light);
}
.hero-kpi .kpi-label{
  font-size:12px;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  font-weight:500;
}

.hero-kpi.big{
  grid-column:1/-1;
  padding:18px 24px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:20px;
}
.hero-kpi.big .kpi-val{ font-size:32px; }

.hero-kpi .kpi-bar{
  height:4px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  border-radius:2px;
  margin-top:10px;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.hero-kpi .kpi-bar-fill{
  height:100%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--blue-light));
  border-radius:2px;
  width:0;
  transition:width 1.6s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   SECTION HEADERS
══════════════════════════════ */
.sec-header{
  display:flex;
  align-items:flex-start;
  gap:20px;
  margin-bottom:50px;
}
.sec-num{
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  font-size:11px;
  color:var(--blue-light);
  font-weight:500;
  padding-top:8px;
  opacity:.7;
  white-space:nowrap;
  letter-spacing:1px;
}
.sec-title h2{
  font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,40px);
  font-weight:800;
  letter-spacing:-0.8px;
  color:#fff;
  line-height:1.1;
  margin-bottom:8px;
}
.sec-title p{
  font-size:15px;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  line-height:1.65;
  max-width:640px;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   DIVIDER
══════════════════════════════ */
.rule{
  height:1px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border2), transparent);
  margin:0;
  border:none;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   OVERVIEW CARDS
══════════════════════════════ */
.overview-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:16px;
  margin-bottom:60px;
}

.ov-card{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:28px 28px 24px;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  transition:.25s;
}
.ov-card::after{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  bottom:0; left:0; right:0;
  height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--blue-light));
  transform:scaleX(0);
  transform-origin:left;
  transition:.3s;
}
.ov-card:hover{ border-color:var(--border2); transform:translateY(-4px); }
.ov-card:hover::after{ transform:scaleX(1); }
.ov-card .ov-icon{ font-size:28px; margin-bottom:14px; }
.ov-card .ov-name{ font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; color:var(--text-dimmer); font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; }
.ov-card .ov-value{ font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   CHALLENGE SECTION
══════════════════════════════ */
.challenge-section{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,60,60,0.04) 0%, rgba(26,86,255,0.04) 100%);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
}

.challenge-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
  gap:16px;
}

.ch-item{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:22px 24px;
  display:flex;
  gap:16px;
  align-items:flex-start;
  transition:.2s;
}
.ch-item:hover{ border-color:rgba(255,100,100,0.25); background:rgba(255,60,60,0.04); }
.ch-icon{
  width:36px; height:36px; flex-shrink:0;
  border-radius:8px;
  background:rgba(255,80,80,0.1);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,80,80,0.15);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:16px;
}
.ch-text .ch-title{ font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:4px; }
.ch-text .ch-desc{ font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.55; }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   SOLUTION SECTION
══════════════════════════════ */
.solution-features{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);
  gap:12px;
  margin-top:40px;
}

.sf-card{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:18px 16px;
  text-align:center;
  transition:.25s;
  cursor:default;
}
.sf-card:hover{
  border-color:var(--border2);
  background:var(--blue-dim);
  transform:translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(26,86,255,0.12);
}
.sf-card .sf-icon{ font-size:24px; margin-bottom:8px; }
.sf-card .sf-label{ font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.4; }

/* Screenshot gallery */
.gallery{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:20px;
  margin:40px 0;
}

.gallery-card{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  overflow:hidden;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:.3s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
  group:true;
}
.gallery-card:hover{ border-color:var(--border2); transform:translateY(-6px); box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(26,86,255,0.15); }
.gallery-card img{ width:100%; height:auto; display:block; }
.gallery-cap{
  padding:14px 18px;
  font-size:13px;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
}
.gallery-cap::before{
  content:'';
  width:6px; height:6px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--blue-light);
  flex-shrink:0;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   TIMELINE
══════════════════════════════ */
.journey-section{
  background:linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(26,86,255,0.04) 50%, transparent 100%);
}

.timeline{
  position:relative;
  padding-left:0;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:0;
}

.tl-item{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:80px 1px 1fr;
  gap:0 24px;
  opacity:0;
  transform:translateY(20px);
  transition:.5s ease;
  position:relative;
}
.tl-item.visible{ opacity:1; transform:none; }

.tl-num{
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
  font-size:11px;
  color:var(--blue-light);
  font-weight:500;
  padding-top:4px;
  text-align:right;
  padding-right:4px;
  opacity:.7;
  line-height:1.4;
}

.tl-spine{
  position:relative;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;
}
.tl-dot{
  width:12px; height:12px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--blue);
  border:2px solid var(--dark);
  box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(26,86,255,0.3);
  flex-shrink:0;
  margin-top:4px;
  z-index:1;
}
.tl-line{
  flex:1;
  width:1px;
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(26,86,255,0.4), rgba(26,86,255,0.1));
  min-height:40px;
}
.tl-item:last-child .tl-line{ display:none; }

.tl-body{
  padding-bottom:36px;
}
.tl-title{
  font-size:16px;
  font-weight:700;
  color:#fff;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}
.tl-desc{
  font-size:14px;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  line-height:1.6;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   CHATBOT DEMO
══════════════════════════════ */
.demo-section{
  background:var(--dark2);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:90px 40px;
  max-width:100%;
}
.demo-inner{ max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; }

.scenario-tabs{
  display:flex;
  gap:8px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  margin-bottom:40px;
}

.s-tab{
  padding:10px 22px;
  border-radius:50px;
  border:1.5px solid var(--border);
  background:transparent;
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:700;
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .2s;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.s-tab:hover{ border-color:var(--blue-light); color:var(--blue-light); }
.s-tab.active{
  border-color:var(--blue);
  background:var(--blue);
  color:#fff;
  box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(26,86,255,0.35);
}

.demo-layout{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:320px 1fr;
  gap:50px;
  align-items:start;
}

/* Phone */
.phone-col{ position:sticky; top:30px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:12px; }

.phone-frame{
  width:300px; height:580px;
  background:#0d0d0d;
  border-radius:46px;
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 1.5px #222,
    0 0 0 8px #111,
    0 0 0 9px #1e1e1e,
    0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6),
    0 0 60px rgba(26,86,255,0.08);
  overflow:hidden;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  border:10px solid #111;
  position:relative;
}
.phone-frame::before{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  top:0; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:110px; height:26px;
  background:#111;
  border-radius:0 0 18px 18px;
  z-index:100;
}
.phone-inner{ width:100%; height:100%; display:flex; flex-direction:column; overflow:hidden; position:relative; background:white; }

.phone-status{
  background:#111;
  color:#fff;
  padding:6px 16px 4px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  font-size:10px;
  height:36px;
  padding-top:22px;
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}

.wa-hdr{
  background:#075E54;
  color:white;
  padding:8px 12px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:10px;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.wa-avatar{
  width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#25D366,#128C7E);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#fff; flex-shrink:0;
  position:relative;
}
.wa-avatar::after{
  content:'✓'; position:absolute; bottom:-1px; right:-2px;
  width:12px; height:12px; background:#25D366; border-radius:50%;
  border:1.5px solid #075E54; font-size:7px; color:#fff;
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; line-height:12px;
}
.wa-hdr-info h3{ font-size:13px; font-weight:700; margin:0; }
.wa-hdr-info p{ font-size:10px; opacity:.75; margin:0; }
.wa-hdr-dots{ margin-left:auto; font-size:16px; opacity:.6; }

.chat-area{
  flex:1; overflow-y:auto; padding:8px 7px;
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1px;
  background-color:#ECE5DD;
  background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='304' height='304' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='%23a09b93' fill-opacity='0.06'%3E%3Cpath d='M56 0h8v16h-8zM24 0h8v16h-8zM88 0h8v16h-8zM0 56V48h16v8zM0 24V16h16v8zM0 88V80h16v8z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  scrollbar-width:none;
}
.chat-area::-webkit-scrollbar{ display:none; }

.wa-chip{
  display:block; width:fit-content;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.87);
  padding:3px 10px; border-radius:6px;
  font-size:10px; font-weight:500; color:#54656F;
  margin:4px auto 5px; box-shadow:0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
  align-self:center;
}

.wa-msg{
  max-width:86%;
  border-radius:8px;
  font-size:12.5px; line-height:1.45;
  color:#111B21;
  position:relative;
  margin-bottom:2px;
  box-shadow:0 1px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
  display:none;
}
.wa-msg.show{ display:block; animation:msgFade .2s ease forwards; }
@keyframes msgFade{
  from{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(4px); }
  to{ opacity:1; transform:none; }
}

.wa-bot{ background:#fff; align-self:flex-start; margin-right:auto; border-top-left-radius:0; }
.wa-bot.first::before{
  content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:-6px;
  border-bottom:7px solid transparent; border-right:6px solid #fff;
}
.wa-user{ background:#D9FDD3; align-self:flex-end; margin-left:auto; border-top-right-radius:0; }
.wa-user.first::before{
  content:''; position:absolute; top:0; right:-6px;
  border-bottom:7px solid transparent; border-left:6px solid #D9FDD3;
}

.msg-body{ padding:5px 8px 2px; word-break:break-word; }

.msg-meta{ display:flex; justify-content:flex-end; align-items:center; gap:2px; padding:0 7px 4px; }
.msg-time{ font-size:9.5px; color:#8696A0; }
.msg-ticks{ font-size:10px; color:#53BDEB; }
.msg-ticks.grey{ color:#8696A0; }

.wa-msg-btns{ border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.09); overflow:hidden; border-radius:0 0 8px 8px; }
.wa-btn{
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:5px;
  padding:8px 10px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:#027EB5;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07); background:#fff;
  cursor:pointer; user-select:none; transition:background .1s;
}
.wa-btn:first-child{ border-top:none; }
.wa-btn.type-reply::before{ content:'↩'; font-size:13px; }
.wa-btn.type-url::before{ content:'↗'; font-size:12px; }
.wa-btn.chosen{ background:#128C7E; color:#fff; pointer-events:none; }
.wa-btn.chosen::before{ color:#fff; }
.wa-btn.unchosen{ color:rgba(2,126,181,0.3); pointer-events:none; }

.wa-typing{
  display:none; align-items:center; gap:3px;
  background:#fff; border-radius:0 8px 8px 8px;
  padding:7px 10px; width:44px; margin-bottom:3px;
  box-shadow:0 1px 0.5px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
  position:relative; align-self:flex-start;
}
.wa-typing::before{
  content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:-6px;
  border-bottom:7px solid transparent; border-right:6px solid #fff;
}
.wa-typing.show{ display:flex; }
.wa-dot{ width:5px; height:5px; background:#8696A0; border-radius:50%; animation:waBounce 1.3s infinite; }
.wa-dot:nth-child(2){ animation-delay:.2s; }
.wa-dot:nth-child(3){ animation-delay:.4s; }
@keyframes waBounce{ 0%,80%,100%{ transform:translateY(0); } 40%{ transform:translateY(-4px); } }

.wa-input-bar{
  background:#f0f2f5; padding:5px 8px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; flex-shrink:0;
}
.wa-input-pill{ flex:1; background:#fff; border-radius:18px; padding:6px 12px; font-size:12px; color:#8696A0; }
.wa-send{ width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:50%; background:#25D366; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#fff; font-size:13px; flex-shrink:0; }

.replay-btn{
  background:transparent;
  border:1.5px solid var(--border);
  color:var(--text-dim);
  border-radius:50px;
  padding:6px 20px;
  font-size:12px;
  font-weight:700;
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:.2s;
}
.replay-btn:hover{ border-color:var(--blue-light); color:var(--blue-light); }

/* Demo info panel */
.demo-info{}
.demo-info-badge{
  display:inline-block;
  font-size:11px; font-weight:700;
  padding:4px 14px; border-radius:50px;
  background:var(--blue-dim); border:1px solid var(--border2);
  color:var(--blue-light); margin-bottom:16px;
  letter-spacing:.5px; text-transform:uppercase;
}
.demo-info h3{ font-size:24px; font-weight:800; color:#fff; margin-bottom:12px; line-height:1.2; }
.demo-info p{ font-size:14px; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:20px; }

.flow-row{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:0;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  margin-bottom:24px;
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:14px 16px;
  gap:6px;
}
.flow-step{
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;
  font-size:12px; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:600;
}
.flow-dot{
  width:20px; height:20px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--surface2); border:1px solid var(--border);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:9px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text-dimmer);
}
.flow-step.done .flow-dot{ background:#10b981; border-color:#10b981; color:#fff; }
.flow-step.done .flow-dot::before{ content:'✓'; }
.flow-step.current .flow-dot{ background:var(--blue); border-color:var(--blue); color:#fff; }
.flow-arr{ color:var(--text-dimmer); font-size:12px; }

.feature-pills{
  display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:24px;
}
.feature-pill{
  font-size:12px; font-weight:600;
  padding:5px 14px; border-radius:50px;
  background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border);
  color:var(--text-dim);
}

.kpi-row{
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px;
}
.kpi-mini{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:16px 18px;
  border-left:3px solid var(--blue);
}
.kpi-mini .k-val{
  font-size:22px; font-weight:800; color:#fff;
  letter-spacing:-0.5px; margin-bottom:2px;
}
.kpi-mini .k-label{
  font-size:11px; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:500;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   RESULTS SECTION
══════════════════════════════ */
.results-section{}

.results-primary{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:16px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

.res-card{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:28px 24px;
  text-align:center;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  cursor:default;
  transition:.25s;
}
.res-card::before{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(26,86,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
  opacity:0;
  transition:.3s;
}
.res-card:hover{ border-color:var(--border2); transform:translateY(-5px); }
.res-card:hover::before{ opacity:1; }

.res-val{
  font-size:46px;
  font-weight:800;
  color:#fff;
  letter-spacing:-2px;
  line-height:1;
  margin-bottom:4px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:flex-end;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:2px;
}
.res-val .rv-unit{
  font-size:24px;
  color:var(--blue-light);
  padding-bottom:4px;
}
.res-label{
  font-size:12px;
  color:var(--text-dim);
  font-weight:600;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:.8px;
  line-height:1.4;
}

.results-secondary{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);
  gap:12px;
  margin-top:16px;
}

.res-mini{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:18px 16px;
  border-top:2px solid var(--blue);
  transition:.2s;
}
.res-mini:hover{ border-color:var(--blue); transform:translateY(-3px); }
.res-mini .rm-val{
  font-size:24px; font-weight:800; color:#fff;
  letter-spacing:-0.5px; margin-bottom:3px;
}
.res-mini .rm-label{
  font-size:11px; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:500;
  line-height:1.4;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   QUOTE SECTION
══════════════════════════════ */
.quote-section{
  background:var(--dark3);
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
}

.quote-card{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,86,255,0.12) 0%, rgba(26,86,255,0.04) 100%);
  border:1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius:24px;
  padding:50px 56px;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.quote-card::before{
  content:'"';
  position:absolute;
  top:-20px; left:36px;
  font-size:160px;
  font-family:Georgia,serif;
  color:rgba(26,86,255,0.12);
  line-height:1;
  pointer-events:none;
}
.quote-card::after{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  right:-80px; top:-80px;
  width:300px; height:300px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,86,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
}

.quote-text{
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:400;
  line-height:1.7;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  margin-bottom:28px;
  max-width:820px;
  position:relative;
  z-index:1;
}

.quote-author{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:14px;
  position:relative;
  z-index:1;
}
.qa-dot{
  width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--blue);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:16px; font-weight:800; color:#fff;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.qa-info .qa-name{ font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; }
.qa-info .qa-role{ font-size:12px; color:var(--text-dim); }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   INSIGHT SECTION
══════════════════════════════ */
.insight-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap:20px;
}

.insight-card{
  background:var(--surface);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:28px;
  transition:.25s;
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.insight-card::after{
  content:'';
  position:absolute;
  top:0; left:0; right:0;
  height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--blue-light));
}
.insight-card:hover{ border-color:var(--border2); transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(26,86,255,0.1); }

.insight-card .ic-emoji{ font-size:32px; margin-bottom:14px; }
.insight-card .ic-title{ font-size:16px; font-weight:800; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px; }
.insight-card .ic-text{ font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.65; }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   FOOTER
══════════════════════════════ */
.site-footer{
  padding:40px;
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  max-width:1180px;
  margin:0 auto;
}
.footer-brand{ font-size:12px; color:var(--text-dimmer); }
.footer-tag{ font-size:11px; color:var(--text-dimmer); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   MODAL
══════════════════════════════ */
.modal{
  display:none; position:fixed; inset:0;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.88); backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  z-index:999; justify-content:center; align-items:center; padding:20px;
}
.modal.open{ display:flex; }
.modal img{ max-width:90vw; max-height:90vh; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.6); }
.modal-close{
  position:absolute; top:20px; right:28px;
  color:white; font-size:34px; cursor:pointer;
  opacity:.7; transition:.2s;
}
.modal-close:hover{ opacity:1; transform:scale(1.15); }

/* ══════════════════════════════
   RESPONSIVE
══════════════════════════════ */
@media(max-width:1000px){
  .hero-inner{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .hero-right{ display:none; }
  section{ padding:60px 24px; }
  .demo-section{ padding:60px 24px; }
  .overview-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .challenge-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .solution-features{ grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); }
  .results-primary{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .results-secondary{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .insight-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .demo-layout{ grid-template-columns:1fr; justify-items:center; }
  .phone-col{ position:static; }
  .quote-card{ padding:32px 28px; }
  .quote-text{ font-size:16px; }
  .gallery{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .kpi-row{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .sec-header{ flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }
  .site-footer{ flex-direction:column; gap:10px; text-align:center; }
}

@media(max-width:640px){
  h1{ font-size:32px; }
  .overview-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .results-primary{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .results-secondary{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .solution-features{ grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
  .hero-inner{ padding:0 24px; }
  .hero-content{ padding:120px 0 80px; }
}

/* ══════════════════════════════
   SCROLL REVEAL
══════════════════════════════ */
.reveal{
  opacity:0;
  transform:translateY(24px);
  transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;
}
.reveal.visible{ opacity:1; transform:none; }
.reveal-delay-1{ transition-delay:.1s; }
.reveal-delay-2{ transition-delay:.2s; }
.reveal-delay-3{ transition-delay:.3s; }
.reveal-delay-4{ transition-delay:.4s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-wrapper">

<!-- ════════ HERO ════════ -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-lines"></div>
  <div class="hero-orb"></div>
  <div class="hero-orb2"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-logos">
          <div class="logo-badge">
            <img src="assets/infobip-logo.png" alt="Infobip" />
            <img class="logo-nissan" src="assets/nissan-logo.svg" alt="Nissan" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-tag">Customer Story</div>
        <h1>
          WhatsApp으로<br/>
          <span class="accent">고객 경험을</span><br/>
          <span class="line2">완전히 재설계하다</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          Nissan Saudi Arabia는 Infobip과 함께 WhatsApp을 단순 메시징이 아닌
          AI 기반 고객 경험 허브로 전환했습니다. 차량 탐색부터 시승 예약까지
          하나의 대화 흐름으로 연결하며 리드와 전환을 동시에 혁신했습니다.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta-row">
          <a href="#chatbot-demo" class="btn-primary">챗봇 체험하기</a>
          <a href="#results" class="btn-ghost">성과 보기 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <div class="hero-stat-cluster">
          <div class="hero-kpi reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="kpi-val"><span class="counter" data-target="138">0</span><span class="unit">%</span></div>
            <div class="kpi-label">리드 생성 증가율</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-kpi reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="kpi-val"><span class="counter" data-target="26">0</span><span class="unit">%</span></div>
            <div class="kpi-label">전환율 (Conversion Rate)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-kpi reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="kpi-val"><span class="counter" data-target="93">0</span><span class="unit">%</span></div>
            <div class="kpi-label">메시지 전달 성공률</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-kpi reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="kpi-val">4.4<span class="unit">/5</span></div>
            <div class="kpi-label">고객 만족도 (CSAT)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-kpi big reveal">
            <div>
              <div class="kpi-val"><span class="counter" data-target="625">0</span><span class="unit">K+</span></div>
              <div class="kpi-label">WhatsApp 메시지 처리</div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:36px;opacity:.3;">💬</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ════════ OVERVIEW ════════ -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-header reveal">
    <div class="sec-num">01 — OVERVIEW</div>
    <div class="sec-title">
      <h2>프로젝트 개요</h2>
      <p>Nissan Saudi Arabia는 단일 채널 중심의 고객 경험을 탈피하여 WhatsApp을 중심으로 한 AI 기반 옴니채널 전략을 실행했습니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="overview-grid">
    <div class="ov-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="ov-icon">💬</div>
      <div class="ov-name">핵심 채널</div>
      <div class="ov-value">WhatsApp Business API</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ov-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="ov-icon">🤖</div>
      <div class="ov-name">솔루션</div>
      <div class="ov-value">AI Conversational Agent (Kaito)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ov-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <div class="ov-icon">🔗</div>
      <div class="ov-name">전략</div>
      <div class="ov-value">Omnichannel Orchestration</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule" />

<!-- ════════ CHALLENGE ════════ -->
<section class="challenge-section">
  <div class="sec-header reveal">
    <div class="sec-num">02 — CHALLENGE</div>
    <div class="sec-title">
      <h2>해결해야 할 과제</h2>
      <p>디지털 전환이 가속화되는 중동 자동차 시장에서 Nissan Saudi Arabia가 직면한 4가지 핵심 문제입니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="challenge-grid">
    <div class="ch-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="ch-icon">⏰</div>
      <div class="ch-text">
        <div class="ch-title">24/7 즉각 응대 불가</div>
        <div class="ch-desc">운영 시간 외 고객 문의가 누락되며 고객 경험이 단절되고 잠재 리드를 놓치는 상황이 반복됐습니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ch-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="ch-icon">🚧</div>
      <div class="ch-text">
        <div class="ch-title">단일 채널 구조의 한계</div>
        <div class="ch-desc">기존 웹·전화 중심 채널로는 모바일 퍼스트 고객층의 참여를 유도하기 어려웠습니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ch-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <div class="ch-icon">📉</div>
      <div class="ch-text">
        <div class="ch-title">디지털 고객 참여율 저조</div>
        <div class="ch-desc">디지털 네이티브 세대를 위한 인터랙티브 경험이 부재해 브랜드 접점에서의 이탈률이 높았습니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ch-item reveal reveal-delay-4">
      <div class="ch-icon">🎯</div>
      <div class="ch-text">
        <div class="ch-title">리드 전환 효율 개선 필요</div>
        <div class="ch-desc">탐색에서 시승 예약까지의 고객 여정이 분절되어 전환율이 업계 평균 이하였습니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule" />

<!-- ════════ SOLUTION ════════ -->
<section>
  <div class="sec-header reveal">
    <div class="sec-num">03 — SOLUTION</div>
    <div class="sec-title">
      <h2>Infobip의 솔루션</h2>
      <p>Infobip은 WhatsApp Business API 기반 AI 챗봇 <strong style="color:#fff;">Kaito</strong>를 구축하여 고객이 차량 탐색부터 시승 예약까지 하나의 대화 흐름 안에서 자연스럽게 이동하도록 설계했습니다. 단순 자동 응답이 아닌, 고객 의도를 이해하고 다음 행동을 연결하는 대화형 고객 경험입니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="gallery">
    <div class="gallery-card reveal reveal-delay-1" onclick="openModal(this.querySelector('img').src)">
      <img src="assets/nissan-ksa-kaito-use-case-1.png" alt="Kaito Chatbot Screenshot 1" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="gallery-cap">Kaito — AI 기반 WhatsApp 대화형 인터페이스</div>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-card reveal reveal-delay-2" onclick="openModal(this.querySelector('img').src)">
      <img src="assets/nissan-ksa-kaito-use-case-2.png" alt="Kaito Chatbot Screenshot 2" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="gallery-cap">WhatsApp Flows 기반 시승 예약 자동화</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="solution-features">
    <div class="sf-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="sf-icon">🕐</div>
      <div class="sf-label">24/7 AI WhatsApp 대화 경험</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sf-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="sf-icon">🚗</div>
